article_id:2110,category_name:News,title_name:Issue Regarding Normal Missions[Update],image_path:,message:<div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1617948600"></span>]</strong></span><br>This issue has been fixed in the data updated applied around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1617948000"></span>.<br>We have also sent the 50 wyrmite endeavor reward to all players who hadn&#39;t completed this endeavor.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><div><br></div><hr><div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Update <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1617946200"></span>]</strong></span><br>The time around which the data update that fixes this issue will be applied was incorrectly noted as <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1617946800"></span>. It should in fact read <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1617948000"></span>.<br><br>Thank you for your understanding.</div><div><br></div><hr><div>We have confirmed that the following issue is occurring since <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1617774000"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>ãƒ»In the Other Normal Endeavors section of the Normal Endeavors, there is an endeavor titled &quot;MISSION_NORMAL_DETAIL_10200001&quot; which can be completed to obtain an endeavor reward.</div><div><br></div><div>This endeavor will be deleted in a data update around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1617946800"></span>.</div><div>After the fix is applied, we will send the 50 wyrmite endeavor reward to all players who haven&#39;t already completed this endeavor.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for your understanding.</div>,start_time:1617792300,update_time1617948715